    <entry>
        <title>Install Jekyll &amp; Deploy to Heroku</title>
        <link href="http://log.tomohiro.me/entries/jekyll-and-heroku"/>
        <updated>2011-03-24T00:00:00+09:00</updated>
        <id>http://log.tomohiro.me/entries/jekyll-and-heroku</id>
        <content type="html">&lt;h3&gt;Install Jekyll&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;gem install jekyll
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h3&gt;Setup&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;mkdir myblog
&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;cd &lt;/span&gt;myblog
&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;touch index.html
&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;mkdir _site _layouts _posts
&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;mkdir css
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h3&gt;Install Rack-Jekyll&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;gem install rack-jekyll
&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;vi config.ru
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;




&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# config.ru&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;rubygems&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;run&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;Rack&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;Jekyll&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;




&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;rack-jekyll&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt; .gems
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;A basic Rack-Jekyll site usually looks something like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;tree
.
|-- .gems
|-- _config.yml
